---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy and Cookies Policy - Mónica Montúfar" description="Privacy and cookies policy of Mónica Montúfar." lang="en">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 min-h-screen">
    <a href="/en" class="text-primary hover:text-white mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 group transition-colors">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined transform group-hover:-translate-x-1 transition-transform">arrow_back</span>
      Back to Home
    </a>

    <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl lg:text-5xl mb-12 text-white">Privacy and Cookies Policy</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-slate max-w-none font-light leading-relaxed text-slate-300">
      <p class="text-sm font-medium text-primary mb-8"><em>Last updated: April 28th, 2026</em></p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl text-white font-serif mt-8 mb-4">1. Personal Data Processing</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        In accordance with current data protection regulations (GDPR and Spanish LOPDGDD), we inform you that the personal data collected through the contact form on this website will be processed with the sole purpose of responding to your inquiry and maintaining communication about the services you have requested. We will not send unsolicited commercial communications (spam), and we safeguard your information with rigorous technical and organizational security standards.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl text-white font-serif mt-8 mb-4">2. Data Collected</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        When you submit the contact form, we collect the following data: first name (required), last name (optional), email address (required), country (optional), and message content (required). This data is processed by <strong>Netlify, Inc.</strong> as form submission handler, under their own privacy policy and data processing agreements.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl text-white font-serif mt-8 mb-4">3. Legal Basis for Processing</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        The legal basis for processing your data is the <strong>consent you provide</strong> by voluntarily submitting the contact form. You may withdraw this consent at any time by contacting us via the email address shown below.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl text-white font-serif mt-8 mb-4">4. Data Retention</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        Your data will be retained only for the time necessary to respond to your inquiry, and in no case longer than <strong>12 months</strong> from the date of receipt, unless a longer retention period is required by applicable law.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl text-white font-serif mt-8 mb-4">5. What Are Cookies?</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        A cookie is a small text file that a website stores on your computer or mobile device when you visit it. We use cookies to understand how you interact with our site, improve your browsing experience, and ensure the correct technical functioning of the website.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl text-white font-serif mt-8 mb-4">6. Types of Cookies We Use</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
        <li><strong>Essential Cookies (Technical):</strong> Strictly necessary for the site to function and cannot be disabled. This includes your cookie consent preference stored locally in your browser.</li>
        <li><strong>Analytical Cookies:</strong> Allow us to count visits and traffic sources to measure and improve site performance. Only enabled if you accept all cookies.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl text-white font-serif mt-8 mb-4">7. Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        This website uses the following third-party services that may process personal data:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
        <li><strong>Netlify</strong> — Hosting and form processing. <a href="https://www.netlify.com/privacy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:text-white transition-colors">Privacy Policy</a></li>
        <li><strong>Google Fonts</strong> — Font loading (Material Symbols). <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:text-white transition-colors">Privacy Policy</a></li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl text-white font-serif mt-8 mb-4">8. Your Rights</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        Under the GDPR and applicable data protection law, you have the right to: access, rectify, erase, or restrict the processing of your personal data; object to its processing; and request data portability. You may also lodge a complaint with the Spanish Data Protection Authority (AEPD) at <a href="https://www.aepd.es" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:text-white transition-colors">www.aepd.es</a>.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-4">
        To exercise any of these rights, please contact us at: <a href="mailto:hola@monicamontufar.com" class="text-primary hover:text-white transition-colors">hola@monicamontufar.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
